<h2>Contents</h2>
</div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="#.E5.8D.87.E7.BA.A7.E6.8C.87.E5.8D.97"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">升级指南</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="#.E5.BF.AB.E9.80.9F.E5.AE.89.E8.A3.9D.E6.8C.87.E5.8D.97"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">快速安裝指南</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="#.E8.AF.A6.E7.BB.86.E5.AE.89.E8.A3.9D.E6.95.99.E5.AD.B8"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">详细安裝教學</span></a></li>
