<h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.8D.87.E7.BA.A7.E6.8C.87.E5.8D.97">升级指南</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: 升级指南" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: 升级指南">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>如果你已经使用 MediaWiki，请参阅<a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Upgrading" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Upgrading">升级指南</a>。</p>
<table class="wikitable" style="margin:.4em .4em .4em .4em; float:right;">
<tr>
<td style="max-width:375px; text-align:left; padding: .4em .4em .4em 1em; font-size:105%; background-color:#EEEEEE;"><a href="/wiki/File:Gnome-system-software-installer.svg" class="image" title="系统要求"><img alt="系统要求" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Gnome-system-software-installer.svg/40px-Gnome-system-software-installer.svg.png" width="40" height="40" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Gnome-system-software-installer.svg/60px-Gnome-system-software-installer.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Gnome-system-software-installer.svg/80px-Gnome-system-software-installer.svg.png 2x" /></a> <span style="font-size:140%; margin-left:10px;"><b><sub>系统要求</sub></b></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 .4em .24em .4em; font-size:95%; max-width:375px;">
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Download" title="Special:MyLanguage/Download">下载</a> MediaWiki（当前稳定版本：1.22.2）</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><b>网页服务器</b>，像是 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://httpd.apache.org">Apache</a>、<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.microsoft.com/iis">IIS</a>
<ul>
<li>本地或命令行权限需要运行日常维护</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><b><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.php.net">PHP</a></b> 5.3.2 或更高版本，但不是 <a href="https://bugzilla.wikimedia.org/show_bug.cgi?id=49975" class="extiw" title="bugzilla:49975">PHP 5.5</a> 的当前版本。<br />
因为 PHP 的一个安全问题而推荐使用 PHP 5.3.5+（<a class="external text" href="//lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/mediawiki-announce/2011-January/000094.html">点击此处以查看详细信息</a>）。
<ul>
<li>需要 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://php.net/pcre">Perl 兼容正则表达式</a></li>
<li>需要 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://php.net/spl">标准 PHP 库</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><b>数据库服务器</b>
<ul>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mysql.com">MySQL</a> 5.0.2 或更高版本（*）</li>
<li>或 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.postgresql.org">PostgreSQL</a> 8.1+
<ul>
<li>需要 PL/pgSQL (contained in contribs)</li>
<li>全文检索（内置 &gt;=8.3，需要 tsearch2 扩展 &lt;=8.2）</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>或 <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/SQLite" title="Special:MyLanguage/SQLite">SQLite</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><small>For <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:image_thumbnailing" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:image thumbnailing">image thumbnailing</a> and <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Texvc" title="Special:MyLanguage/Texvc">TeX</a>-support, additional programs are required.</small></p>
<p><small>(*) – <a href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MariaDB" class="extiw" title="w:MariaDB">MariaDB</a>, a <a href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GPL" class="extiw" title="w:GPL">GPL</a> fork of the MySQL code by Monty Widenius, the founder of MySQL, is an alternative and can also be used by MediaWiki. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://downloads.askmonty.org/mariadb/repositories/">Debian/Ubuntu repos</a>.</small></p>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.BF.AB.E9.80.9F.E5.AE.89.E8.A3.9D.E6.8C.87.E5.8D.97">快速安裝指南</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: 快速安裝指南" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: 快速安裝指南">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<table style="background-color: #F5A9A9;">
<tr>
<td><b>通过主机服务商自动安装时的问题</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>通过主机服务商提供的程序可以自动安装像 MediaWiki 这样的应用，并且运行得很频繁，影响安装进度，导致 MediaWiki 安装失败（或影响到其他应用）。如果你遇到这个问题，<b>并不</b>意味着你不能 MediaWiki，你需要手动安装。这是一个简单而且有益的做法，包含了更多指定服务器和路径的操作、使用共享数据库的条件，或者在安装过程中定制 wiki 的更多功能。</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>For experienced users, here is the quick version of the installation instructions. Most users will want to read the more detailed version, <a href="#Main-installation-guide">below</a>.</p>
<ol>
<li>檢查你的系統是否符合<a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_requirements/zh&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Manual:Installation requirements/zh (page does not exist)">最低系統要求</a>。</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Download" title="Special:MyLanguage/Download">下载 MediaWiki</a> <small><a href="http://download.wikimedia.org/mediawiki/1.22/mediawiki-1.22.2.tar.gz" class="extiw" title="download:mediawiki/1.22/mediawiki-1.22.2.tar.gz">（直接下载最新稳定版）</a></small>，然后解压缩到你服务器的网络存储文件夹。</li>
<li>指向你的浏览器到安装目录（例如：<tt>http://[domain]/mediawiki/index.php</tt>）。如果你安装在本地设备上，请把 [domain] 改成 <b>localhost</b>。如果你安装在远程服务器上，请把 [domain] 你的主机域名，比如 www.myserver.com。</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Config_script" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Config script">跟着屏幕的安装提示</a>直到完成。</li>
</ol>
<p>上述安装提示只是一个简要说明，也许会出错，所以，如果有任何不确定的地方，建议你还是阅读下面的完整安装说明。</p>
<p><span id="Main-installation-guide"></span></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".E8.AF.A6.E7.BB.86.E5.AE.89.E8.A3.9D.E6.95.99.E5.AD.B8">详细安裝教學</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: 详细安裝教學" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: 详细安裝教學">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>安裝前
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:What_is_MediaWiki%3F" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:What is MediaWiki?">了解Mediawiki是甚麼</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:MediaWiki_feature_list" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:MediaWiki feature list">查看MediaWiki功能清单</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installation_requirements" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installation requirements">系統需求</a> - 在向下进行前务必查看！</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing_MediaWiki" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing MediaWiki">安裝MediaWiki</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>配置MediaWiki:
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Config_script" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Config script">初始配置</a>（使用配置脚本）</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Configuring_MediaWiki" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Configuring MediaWiki">更多的配置</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing_extensions" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing extensions">安裝額外插件</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Alternative_to_manual_installation">Alternative to manual installation</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Alternative to manual installation" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Alternative to manual installation">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>Some users may prefer to skip manual installation by using a pre-integrated MediaWiki <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Software_appliances" title="Special:MyLanguage/Software appliances">software appliance</a> or <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Hosting_services" title="Special:MyLanguage/Hosting services">hosting services with 1-click installation and wiki farms</a>.</p>
<p>If you are installing only for <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/How_to_become_a_MediaWiki_hacker" title="Special:MyLanguage/How to become a MediaWiki hacker">development</a> or testing, consider using <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/mediawiki-vagrant" title="Special:MyLanguage/mediawiki-vagrant">mediawiki-vagrant</a>. You must have (and enable) <a href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/hardware_virtualization" class="extiw" title="w:hardware virtualization">hardware virtualization</a>. Many modern computers have this, and you can check in your BIOS.</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".E9.99.84.E5.BD.95">附录</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: 附录" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: 附录">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
