</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Running_MediaWiki_on_Windows" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Running MediaWiki on Windows">Windows</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing_MediaWiki_on_Windows_XP" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing MediaWiki on Windows XP">Windows XP</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing_MediaWiki_on_Windows_Server_2003" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing MediaWiki on Windows Server 2003">Windows Server 2003</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing_MediaWiki_on_Windows_Server_2008" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing MediaWiki on Windows Server 2008">Windows Server 2008</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing_MediaWiki_on_Windows_Server_2008_R2" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Installing MediaWiki on Windows Server 2008 R2">Windows Server 2008 R2</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Newcomers_guide_to_installing_on_Windows" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Newcomers guide to installing on Windows">Newcomers guide</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Streamlined_Windows_Install_Guide" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Streamlined Windows Install Guide">Streamlined Guide</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Simple_Windows_Apache_Installation" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Simple Windows Apache Installation">Simple Windows Apache Installation</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".E6.B3.A8.E6.84.8F">注意</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: 注意" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: 注意">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="plainlinks">
<ul>
<li>MediaWiki 附带安装工具，以方便您通过浏览器来完成安装</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>MediaWiki 可以和其它程序共用一个数据库，例如 phpBB</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>如果您想修改 MediaWiki 的内部逻辑的话，您需要懂 PHP 编程</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>MediaWiki 1.7 之后的版本只能运行在 PHP 5 或更高的版本上。如果您的 PHP 版本低于5，那么您就不可以用 MediaWiki 1.7 及以后的版本了，您得用 MediaWiki 1.6.12 <small><a class="external text" href="http://download.wikimedia.org/mediawiki/1.6/mediawiki-1.6.12.tar.gz">(点击下载)</a></small>. 注意，该版本<i>不再更新</i>。</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>MediaWiki 1.6 之后的版本只能运行在 MySQL 4 或更高的版本上。如果您的 MySQL 版本低于4，那么您就不可以用 MediaWiki 1.6 及以后的版本了，您得用 MediaWiki 1.5.8 <small><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/wikipedia/mediawiki-1.5.8.tar.gz?download">(点击下载)</a></small>。注意，该版本<i>不再更新</i>。</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>MySQL 5 support is required since <a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/MediaWiki_1.19" title="Special:MyLanguage/MediaWiki 1.19">MediaWiki 1.19</a> – if you are using an older version of MySQL and cannot upgrade, you should use MediaWiki 1.18.5 <small>(<a href="http://download.wikimedia.org/mediawiki/1.18/mediawiki-1.18.5.tar.gz" class="extiw" title="download:mediawiki/1.18/mediawiki-1.18.5.tar.gz">download</a>)</small>. Note that this version is <i>no longer supported</i>.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Some users find it helpful to install an additional software package such as <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.phpmyadmin.net">phpMyAdmin</a> (MySQL) or <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://phppgadmin.sourceforge.net/">phpPgAdmin</a> (Postgres) to help administer the database server.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.85.B6.E5.AE.83.E5.8F.82.E8.80.83.E8.B5.84.E6.96.99">其它参考资料</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: 其它参考资料" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/zh-hans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: 其它参考资料">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
